the mathematical model calculates the density of the cells (in 1D) integrating over various concentrations in space and time. the relevant variables are cell migration (browninan motion) cell-cell adhesion (bound cg1 + all bound cg1 in a sensing radio) binding of galectins to receptors and the not bound receptors.


